formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: 1. The variation of expenditure certified to be incurred by Architect and Engineer and expenditure incurred and paid certified by Chartered Accountant is bound to be there as physical progress of project is always at different level then reporting of invoices and expenses bills in financial accounts as they are accounted and when received. Further the project is complete as per certificate given by Architect and variation is expenses incurred on construction and interest is explained as per notes to certificate . Subject to that, there is coherence between progress of project as well as incurrence and payment of expenses considering project specification.
